<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7741493>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Larva of Centroptilum volodymyri sp. nov., Georgia, holotype. (a, b), Body in lateral view. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7741493/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7741495>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Larva of Centroptilum volodymyri sp. nov., Iran. (a) Body in dorsal view; (b) body in lateral view; (c) head and part of thorax in lateral view. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7741495/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7741497>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Larvae of Centroptilum volodymyri sp. nov., paratype (a, c, e) and C. luteolum (Müller, 1776) (b, d, f). (a, b) Scapus and pedicellus; (c) flagellum, basal part; (d) flagellum, central part; (e, f) surface of frons. Scale bars: a, c, d = 20 μm; b = 30 μm; e = 10 μm; f = 100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7741497/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7741499>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Larvae of Centroptilum volodymyri sp. nov., paratype (a–e) and C. luteolum (Müller, 1776) (f). (a) Labrum; (b) galea-lacinia; (c, d) mandibles, left (c) and right (d); (e, f) maxillary palp. Scale bars: a, b, e, f = 30 μm; c, d = 100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7741499/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7741501>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Larvae of Centroptilum volodymyri sp. nov., paratypes. (a, b) Labrum, ventral (a) and dorsal (b) view; (c) hypopharynx (left side – dorsal view; right side – ventral view); (d, e) glossa and paraglossa, dorsal (d) and ventral (e) view; (f) maxilla; (g, h) labial palp, ventral (g) and dorsal (h) view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7741501/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7741503>
    dc:description "Figure 6. Larvae of Centroptilum volodymyri sp. nov., paratype (a, c, e) and C. luteolum (Müller, 1776) (b, d, f). (a, b) Pronotum, dorsal surface; (c, d) hind femur, dorsal surface; (e, f) hind tibia, dorsal surface. Scale bars: a–c, e, f = 30 μm; d = 10 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7741503/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7741507>
    dc:description "Figure 8. Larvae of Centroptilum volodymyri sp. nov., paratypes. (a) Fore leg; (b) middle leg; (c) hind leg." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7741507/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7741505>
    dc:description "Figure 7. Larvae of Centroptilum volodymyri sp. nov., paratype (a, c, e, g) and C. luteolum (Müller, 1776) (b, d, f). a, b = hind pretarsal claw (apex of claw not visible in (a)); (c, d) denticles of hind pretarsal claw; (e) surface of sternum IV; (f) surface and posterior margin of sternum VI; (g) surface and posterior margin of sternum VII. Scale bars: a = 50 μm; b = 100 μm; c–e, g = 30 μm; f = 10 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7741505/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7741509>
    dc:description "Figure 9. Larvae of Centroptilum volodymyri sp. nov., paratype (a, c, e, g) and C. luteolum (Müller, 1776) (b, d, f, h). Surfaces and posterior margins of terga: (a, b) tergum II; (c, d) tergum IV; (e, f) tergum VI; (g, h) tergum VIII. Scale bars: a, b = 20 μm; c–h = 30 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7741509/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7741511>
    dc:description "Figure 10. Larvae of Centroptilum volodymyri sp. nov., paratypes. (a) Gill I; (b) gill II; (c) gill III; (d) gill IV; (e) gill V; (f) gill VI; (g) gill VII; (h) posterolateral part of tergum VII; (i) paraproct plate." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7741511/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7741513>
    dc:description "Figure 11. Larvae of Centroptilum volodymyri sp. nov., paratype (a, c, e) and C. luteolum (Müller, 1776) (b, d, f). (a, b) Apical part of paraproct; (c) surface of paraproct; (d) tergum X and caudal filaments; (e) caudal filaments, basal part; (f) caudal filament, medial part. Scale bars: a, b, e, f = 30 μm; c = 20 μm; d = 100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7741513/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7741515>
    dc:description "Figure 12. Eggs of Centroptilum volodymyri sp. nov., from paratype (a, c, e, g) and C. luteolum (Müller, 1776) (b, d, f, h); provided by Nicolás Ubero-Pascal). (a–d) General view of egg; (e, f) chorionic surface; (g, h) micropyle. Scale bars: a, c = 30 μm; b = 80 μm; d = 20 μm; e, g = 5 μm; f = 10 μm; h = 5 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7741515/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7741517>
    dc:description "Figure 13. Habitats of Centroptilum volodymyri sp. nov. in Georgia, Iran and Turkey. (a, b) Small lentic waterbody, Georgia, Adjara, type locality (April 2016; photos by A. Martynov); (c, d) small brook, left tributary of Shalmanrud River, Guilan Province, Iran (May 2016; photos by J. Bojková); (e, f) small stream, Rize Province, Turkey (August 2012; photos by D. Palatov)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7741517/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7741524>
    dc:description "Figure 15. Maximum likelihood tree including several representatives of the genus Centroptilum. Bootstrap supports (BS) are indicated on branches for Centroptilum volodymyri sp. nov. and C. luteolum (Müller, 1776)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7741524/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

